{"tid":2024432,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"<燭光遍地>支聯會：傾向以「遍地開花」悼六四","createTime":"2020-05-19T15:12:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-19T15:23:48.000Z","uid":227801,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fcddc97bba1db910ea9885371f393639837eafa7","tid":2024432,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T15:12:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1527129-20200519.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1527129-20200519.htm&d=Vmg9VhgMmKCDk1oLDtgP7vY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=db050009\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1527129-20200519.htm&h=44d0aa75\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1527129-20200519.htm</a><br />\n政府宣布限聚令將延長至6月4日，主辦維園六四燭光晚會的支聯會會開會後，決定繼續申請集會及遊行，但會作兩手準備，一旦無法在維園舉行燭光晚會，會以「遍地開花」的形式進行悼念<br />\n<br />\n支聯會主席李卓人表示，無法預計參與的市民會否因限聚令被檢控，會提醒參加者保持距離。支聯會在5月24日的長跑會如常舉行。<br />\n<br />\n李卓人表示，防疫措施進一步放寬，政府一方面決定如期復課及准許宗教活動，卻不容許舉辦集會，質疑是有政治考慮、「趁疫打劫」。李卓人說，現時最大問題是場地，亦未知警方會否批准不反對通知書。<br />\n<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥今早表示，是否延長社交距離限制，只考慮公眾安全及公共衛生，不會有政治考慮。"},{"pid":"e8ce45b0726106ab1b0f4aac7148b5aae313f6b6","tid":2024432,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T15:14:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec7a1f637a38d64a1b645dd43a18b8facc147ded","tid":2024432,"uid":1989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T15:15:10.000Z","msg":"識玩"},{"pid":"58cd29889e8b265bed12fa4833d7e607779fe348","tid":2024432,"uid":227801,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ec7a1f637a38d64a1b645dd43a18b8facc147ded","tid":2024432,"uid":1989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T15:15:10.000Z","msg":"識玩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T15:16:07.000Z","msg":"週街黑警= 重演六四"},{"pid":"aaa5654c337050675f139570aac709c2319c08d5","tid":2024432,"uid":68111,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ec7a1f637a38d64a1b645dd43a18b8facc147ded","tid":2024432,"uid":1989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T15:15:10.000Z","msg":"識玩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T15:16:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />諗下好啦 李卓人之流咁多年都......<br />\n最後又會話好黑暗 叫你忍耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25acb807a7da816c75cb5449fe909895e10f3329","tid":2024432,"uid":2054,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T15:17:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">全港商場悼六四</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/b/bf/Incendo_Panorama1_%2848464029416%29.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fb%2Fbf%2FIncendo_Panorama1_%252848464029416%2529.jpg&h=f11f5c57&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d73df2a97cdf7074f1b7fb07434c6b7d310a4401","tid":2024432,"uid":23085,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T15:17:43.000Z","msg":"連支聯會都開花<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afb27d2f86cd90c7c99d8da260f1139d90097dcd","tid":2024432,"uid":103916,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T15:19:07.000Z","msg":"鬼節......燒元寶蠟燭"},{"pid":"670fe613277622f7f0a016d841bf2755890caaea","tid":2024432,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T15:23:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f60e55504744907776bb0fbba4a72b681a6215d","tid":2024432,"uid":333488,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05